title: Imperial Leisure Discography (2008 - 2014) MP3
description:
Imperial Leisure are a high energy altska band from London busting out skanktastic, catchy tunes with big brass and big attitude.

Together for more than 10 years, Imperial Leisure are champions of the arena. With countless live gigs and festivals under their belt, Imperial Leisure never fail to deliver a awesome show.
